title: Discover Islam CD [SMalki]
description:
Short Description: A variety of well picked materials (Audios,Videos, Books ..etc) in English Language suited for non-Muslims. Gathered in a CD/DVD user-friendly application which can be easily burned for distribution purposes.
Just Select all the RAR files (as shown in figure 1) and extract them to a folder using WinRAR. Then all you have to do is burn these files to a CD or DVD.


This CD is produced by IslamHouse.com
